Unwilling to take no for an answer, young Parker gets on his knees to show the coach just how much he wants to get in. Tanner's attention goes straight to the athlete's fresh hole where he puts Parker to the test. After a series of huge dildos, anal beeds and eventually Tanner's fist, Parker just might make the big leagues after all!
